<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.5">
<l>aṉṉaimuṉivatu maṉṟiliṉkura līrvatum</l>
<l>maṉṉumaṟikaṭa lārppatumvaḷai cōrvatum</l>
<l>poṉṉaṅkalaiyal kulaṉṉameṉṉaṭaip pūṅkuḻal</l>
<l>piṉṉaimaṇāḷar tiṟattamāyiṉa piṉṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mother raging, the black ibis’s voice grating,</l>
<l>The roaring of the eternal roiling sea, and [my] bangles slipping,</l>
<l>[All happened] after we were beside the beloved of Piṉṉai,</l>
<l>With a lovely gold-girdled waist, a slow swan[-like] gait, and flowery curls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
